---
title: Warm Barley Salad with Great Northern Beans, Avocado, and Burst Tomatoes
description: We love a good grain salad – it’s all about the mix-ins! Here, we’re tossing together creamy beans, silky avocado, and burst tomatoes for a mixture of colors and textures. Torn basil adds a touch of lemony freshness to the dish.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/570c0c4df8b25ee23e8b4567.jpg
